(-1)^{n+1}\frac{3}{5^n}=-3\frac{(-1)^{n}}{5^{n}}=-3\left(\frac{-1}{5}\right)^{n}
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}-3\left(\frac{-1}{5}\right)^{n}=\frac{-3\cdot\frac{-1}{5}}{1-\frac{-1}{5}}=\frac{\frac{3}{5}}{\frac{6}{5}}=\frac{1}{2}
